NiceText (JavaScript port)
==========================

The MIT license below covers all original work in this repository.

Third-party materials are deliberately confined to two directories,
`fixture-src/` and `fixtures/`: Project Gutenberg texts, the CMU
Pronouncing Dictionary, the MIT names list, Moby Project files,
WordNet, Unicode data (emoji, CLDR, TR39 confusables), the Apple II
Screen font, and other corpora and data sources. These retain their
original licenses and are identified in `attributions.html`. Nothing
outside `fixture-src/` and `fixtures/` is third-party. (Those two
directories also hold project-authored material, build configs,
curated and Claude-authored lists, and our derived artifacts, which
are MIT like the rest.)

